headline: Rockwell Automation Launches EtherNet/IP In-cabinet Solution to Help Manufacturers Build Smarter, More Efficient Panels
summary: Rockwell Automation, Inc. (NYSE: ROK), the world's largest company dedicated to industrial automation and digital transformation, today announced the release of its EtherNet/IP™ In-cabinet Solution, a major advancement designed to meet the growing demand for smarter, faster and more connected manufacturing operations.

headline: Q1 Earnings Outperformers: SmartRent (NYSE:SMRT) And The Rest Of The Internet of Things Stocks
summary: As the Q1 earnings season wraps, let’s dig into this quarter’s best and worst performers in the internet of things industry, including SmartRent (NYSE:SMRT) and its peers.
